ode\"<ref name=\":7\" />\n| align=\"center\" | \u2014\n|}\n\n== Notes ==\n{{notelist-ua}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:New Zealand heavy metal musical groups]]\n", "name_user": "Theevinco", "label": "safe", "comment": "Including label details.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Devilskin"}
